    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nA(30;-30) \\in (P_1) \\Rightarrow 30^2 \\cdot a + 30 = -30 \\Leftrightarrow a = \\frac{-1}{15} \\Rightarrow (P_1): y = \\frac{-1}{15}x^2 + 30.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
