    "text": "$$\n\\Rightarrow C(x) = -48x_1 \\left( \\frac{-1}{15}x_1^2 + 30 \\right) + 72000 = \\frac{16}{5}x_1^3 - 1440x_1 + 72000 \\quad (0 \\le x_1 \\le 30)\n$$"
  },
  {
