    "text": "$$\n\\Rightarrow C'(x) = \\frac{48}{5}x_1^2 - 1440 = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x_1 = 5\\sqrt{6} \\in [0;30] \\\\ x_1 = -5\\sqrt{6} \\notin [0;30] \\end{cases}\n$$"
